### SEC 10-K RAG API — sample requests
# Requires the "REST Client" VS Code extension (humao.rest-client).
# Start the server first (F5, or: uvicorn main:app --reload), then click
# the "Send Request" link that appears above each request below.

@base = http://127.0.0.1:8000

### Health check
GET {{base}}/health

### Ingest Apple 2025 10-K
POST {{base}}/documents/ingest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/320193/000032019325000079/aapl-20250927.htm",
  "company_name": "Apple",
  "doc_id": "aapl-2025"
}

### Ingest Microsoft 2025 10-K (for cross-company questions)
POST {{base}}/documents/ingest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/789019/000095017025100235/msft-20250630.htm",
  "company_name": "Microsoft",
  "doc_id": "msft-2025"
}

### Ingest NVIDIA 2025 10-K
POST {{base}}/documents/ingest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1045810/000104581025000023/nvda-20250126.htm",
  "company_name": "NVIDIA",
  "doc_id": "nvda-2025"
}

### List all ingested documents
GET {{base}}/documents

### Get extracted sections for Apple (full text: add ?preview_chars=0)
GET {{base}}/documents/aapl-2025/sections

### Q&A — top business risks
POST {{base}}/questions/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What are the top business risks described by the company?",
  "top_k": 5
}

### Q&A — revenue growth / performance
POST {{base}}/questions/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What does the company say about revenue growth or business performance?",
  "top_k": 5
}

### Q&A — scoped to one company
POST {{base}}/questions/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What are the main business segments or operating priorities?",
  "company_filter": "Apple",
  "top_k": 5
}

### Q&A — compare risk factors between two companies
POST {{base}}/questions/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Compare the risk factors between Apple and Microsoft.",
  "section_filter": "Risk Factors",
  "top_k": 8
}

### Async analysis job — submit a batch of questions
# @name createJob
POST {{base}}/analysis-jobs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "questions": [
    "What are the top business risks?",
    "What themes appear repeatedly in management discussion?"
  ]
}

### Poll an analysis job (paste the job_id returned above)
GET {{base}}/analysis-jobs/{{createJob.response.body.job_id}}
